data.description: Pre-Inspection is done, saving your Buyer money and Seller is ready for your negotiations! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom, tri-level home has a large kitchen leading to an open concept living room and dining room.  Large windows fill the home with light and the recreation room downstairs off the dining room is designed for passive solar gain and has a wood stove.  Three bedrooms upstairs with one full bath for the two spare bedrooms.  The primary bedroom has a ¾ bath as well as a small deck.  Downstairs is a large bedroom suite with a private closet, laundry room and ¾ bath that could be used in a variety of ways. The roof was replaced in September 2023 with a transferable warranty. Seller is offering a $5,000 carpet credit with reasonable offer. Welcome home.
